options.text: , this one-day event at Stanford brings together builders, researchers, students, developers and the open-source Flower community to explore what's possible with decentralized AI. Through hands-on building, lightning talks, and demo/poster sessions, you'll connect with others advancing decentralized intelligence. Additional event details are available

large.fontFamily: degular, -apple-system, "system-ui", "Apple Color Emoji", Inter, Roboto, "Segoe UI", "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif

options.text: Decentralized is the next big thing in AI. Bring your ideas, learn more about this tech (or share your skills with others). Get feedback from experts on-hand to help.
Share your existing project or learn from the work of others. Lightning talks and demo/poster sessions throughout the day.
Connect with the decentralized and federated AI community during the event. Food, swag and fun will be available at all times.
Hackathon teams will compete for $2,500+ in prizes.
